biogHist.abstract: Current Practice Workshop 4 - Who Am I? Learning and Development for record keeping to support identity: from accountability to identity construction and meaning-making was the fourth workshop in the current practice stand of The Who Am I? Project. The workshop was held on 23 October 2009.
